o Kings]]|years=2015&ndash;present | after= Incumbent}}\n{{S-end}}\n{{KK Partizan 1988\u201389 FIBA Kora\u0107 Cup Champions}}\n{{Yugoslavia Squad 1986 FIBA World Championship}}\n{{Yugoslavia Squad EuroBasket 1987}}\n{{Footer 1988 Olympic Silver Medalists Basketball Men}}\n{{Yugoslavia Squad EuroBasket 1989}}\n{{Yugoslavia Squad 1990 FIBA World Championship}}\n{{Yugoslavia Squad EuroBasket 1991}}\n{{Yugoslavia Squad EuroBasket 1995}}\n{{Footer 1996 Olympic Silver Medalists Basketball Men}}\n{{Yugoslavia Squad EuroBasket 1999}}\n{{Yugoslavia Squad 2002 FIBA World Championship}}\n{{Sacramento Kings}}\n{{Mr. Europa|state=collapsed}}\n{{FIBA50}}\n{{Euroleague50}}\n{{1989 NBA Draft}}\n{{J. Walter Kennedy Citizenship Award}}\n{{FIBA Hall of Fame}}\n{{Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame}}\n{{2019 Basketball HOF}}\n}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Divac, Vlade}}\n[[Category:1968 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:2002 FIBA World Championship players]]\n[[Category:Basketball players at the 1988 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Basketball players at the 1996 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Centers (basketball)]]\n[[Category:Charlotte Hornets players]]\n[[Category:FIBA EuroBasket-winning players]]\n[[Category:FIBA Hall of Fame inductees]]\n[[Category:FIBA World Championship-winning players]]\n[[Category:KK Crvena zvezda players]]\n[[Category:KK Partizan players]]\n[[Category:KK Sloga players]]\n[[Category:Los Angeles Lakers draft picks]]\n[[Category:Los Angeles Lakers players]]\n[[Category:Los Angeles Lakers scouts]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 1988 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 1996 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame inductees]]\n[[Category:National Basketball Association All-Stars]]\n[[Category:National Basketball Association general managers]]\n[[Category:National Basketball Association players from Serbia]]\n[[Category:National Basketball Association players with retired numbers]]\n[[Category